Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:53.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}自分の過去に囚われ迷って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:58.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}そうじゃないよと　言い聞かせて　全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:03.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}自由に操れるかなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}分からないよと　空は霞んで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}正解はどこ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:14.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}僕の手のひらに　残る大事なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:18.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}忘れない記憶　何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:24.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}君を守り抜くと叫んで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:29.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}巻き戻しの中　掴んだ愛は　そう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}離しはしないから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:36.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}散りばめた想い　今一度きりの願いへ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:41.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}次への僕に　託したよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:46.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}いつかの約束　光の道しるべになる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:57.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}誓いをさあ　君のため　最期まで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:02.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}涙さえ力に変えてきっと　描いていた望む未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}繋ぐよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:53.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}無法擺脫自己過去的束縛  迷失了前進方向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:58.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}還自欺述說那並不是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:03.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}不知道這些是否能自由控制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}天色為何又如此朦朧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}答案又在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:14.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}雙手還殘留著有什麼很重要的事尚未完成的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:18.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}這段記憶將塵封於心  永久保存
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:24.03,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}誓要將你保護到底的決心已化作言語放聲吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:29.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}回放逝去的倒帶  把對你永恆的摯愛捧在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.37,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}定不會輕易放手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:36.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}這是最後一次請求  將這散落一地的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:41.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}託付給未來的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:46.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}曾經的約定  化作黎明的燈塔指引我前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:57.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我發誓將為了你支撐到最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:02.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}連淚水也化作力量  一定會將心中描繪的所期待的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}與現實銜接
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:42.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.79,0:22:44.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:50.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:52.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:02.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}狂った時計　刻む命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:06.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれてく記憶の砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:09.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}芽生えた想いまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:14.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:22.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:23.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish I was there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:25.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:27.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:32.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度となにも失くさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:38.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私を忘れて　始めて　Restart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.02,0:23:41.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:43.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:47.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:53.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:56.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:00.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:02.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.46,0:24:03.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:07.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:10.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.22,0:24:11.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:42.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}請不要讓我離開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.79,0:22:44.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的觸碰  我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:50.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不  請不要對生命無愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:52.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}儘管這絕望  不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:02.23,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}失準的時鐘  記錄著生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:06.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}散落滿地的記憶之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:09.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:14.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你看  卻是那麼輕易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:22.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消失殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:23.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我希望能與你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:25.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}請不要讓我離開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:27.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的觸碰  我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:32.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}為了不再失去曾經擁有的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:38.93,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}讓我忘卻自己的過去  重新開始旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.02,0:23:41.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不  請不要對生命無愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:43.23,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}儘管這絕望  不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:47.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}願那讓你苦不堪言的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:53.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}會迎來完結的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:56.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而我卻要目送你離開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:00.29,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們終將會重來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:02.37,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重來對新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.46,0:24:03.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:07.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們終將會重來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:10.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重來對新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.22,0:24:11.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}與你攜手邁進
